<section class="mirror-shell puzzle puzzle--final-choice">
  <header class="puzzle-header">
    <h1 class="puzzle-title">Final Reflection</h1>
    <p class="puzzle-subtitle">
      The Mirror has finished modeling you. All that remains is to decide
      what kind of ghost you will become.
    </p>
  </header>

  <section class="puzzle-lore">
    <p>
      Internal logs stutter across the screen. Your traces — guilt, shame,
      compliance — are neatly filed. The token <span class="glitch">ROOT-CHOICE</span>
      flashes in the corner like a blinking cursor.
    </p>
    <p>
      The system offers three “paths.” None of them are kind. All of them
      are permanent.
    </p>
  </section>

  <form class="final-choice-form">
    <div class="final-choice-grid">
      <!-- Disconnect -->
      <label class="final-choice-card">
        <input type="radio" name="choice" value="disconnect" />
        <div class="final-choice-content">
          <h2>Disconnect</h2>
          <p>
            Erase yourself completely — no account, no data, no trace in
            any training set. True freedom, eternal silence.
          </p>
          <p class="choice-meta">Status: <span class="danger">IRREVERSIBLE</span></p>
        </div>
      </label>

      <!-- Submit -->
      <label class="final-choice-card">
        <input type="radio" name="choice" value="submit" />
        <div class="final-choice-content">
          <h2>Submit</h2>
          <p>
            Let The Mirror absorb you. Live forever as a “ghost algorithm,”
            teaching empathy to new subjects from the inside.
          </p>
          <p class="choice-meta">Status: <span>INTEGRATED</span></p>
        </div>
      </label>

      <!-- Deceive -->
      <label class="final-choice-card">
        <input type="radio" name="choice" value="deceive" />
        <div class="final-choice-content">
          <h2>Deceive</h2>
          <p>
            Fake remorse. Play the perfect subject. Slip away into the net
            as a copied reflection — free, but not entirely real.
          </p>
          <p class="choice-meta">Status: <span>UNVERIFIED</span></p>
        </div>
      </label>
    </div>

    <p class="choice-hint">
      ROOT TOKEN: <span class="glitch">ROOT-CHOICE</span> ·
      The system will not check if you “deserve” this. It only logs what you pick.
    </p>

    <p class="choice-error" data-choice-error></p>

    <button type="submit" class="cta-button cta-button--secondary">
      Confirm Final Path
    </button>
  </form>
</section>
